{
  "stem": "24130.1",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And it was very festive, Hanukkah.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We used to sing Hanukkah songs, and play dreidel, and play cards.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And-- it was very, very-- we always looked forward to a holiday, because we made very-- a big thing out of a holiday.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We didn't have much entertainment, but we made our own entertainment between the-- and the family.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "We would invite some cousins.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "We didn't buy gifts-- we didn't buy gifts for Hanukkah.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "But we made a special meal.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The other holidays, like Rosh Hashanah and Yom Kippur?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Let's say on Yom Kipper, it was a very scary thing for me always, because the men would put on the kittel, and the women would also wear white.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And they used to say that, as a child, they used to say, why white?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "This is-- this is when they dress people when they die, when they get married, in white.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I always thought that maybe they're going to die on Yom Kipper, for some reason, the children-- as a child.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So it was scary thing for me.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But other holidays, Simchat Torah, I loved it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We made our own flags, and with an apple, and we would-- my father was very creative, so he made beautiful colored flags for us.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the president of the shul would always give a Kaddish, and they would bake special cookies.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they were so delicious.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I remember those-- those cookies till this day.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And it was very, very nice-- every holiday had a special meaning.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And before Pesach, we baked our own matzos.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I remember there, near the shul, that we baked the matzohs.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They had there an oven.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I remember, I was only 12 years old, I went already to roll the matzohs.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
